{"tid":1817431,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"(行動)1月11全民連儂日，有隻雀仔話都想出一分力","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T00:38:43.000Z","uid":236459,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61ac8bb0b956469fce938318f20beebc2d04f9a4","tid":1817431,"uid":236459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"1月11你唸住點過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如約班朋友摺下紙，行下連儂牆聯誼感情！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezEGBPR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezEGBPR.png&h=085be9fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52ejoC2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52ejoC2.png&h=62e22fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwiL3DV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwiL3DV.png&h=02d3c9dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2THAGqZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2THAGqZ.png&h=d5594258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻雀話佢到時會自動飛去元天屯，再放啲紙俾人攞嚟摺<br />\n有冇人想幫手去其他連儂牆幫手放低啲影印本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有嘅tg搵FayFayRR<br />\n呢個傻閪會順手俾埋上個po隻雀你！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZHtgZz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZHtgZz.jpg&h=6fa706cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZkys6M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZkys6M.png&h=21c6ccb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說好掛住學校啲printer，原來出面印嘢好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得出嚟啦！！！！！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b70c3ade1170ca81a2327da7f264ed73be39a6","tid":1817431,"uid":236459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-0